{"id":2375,"date":"2025-05-13T15:55:51","date_gmt":"2025-05-13T08:55:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2375"},"modified":"2025-05-15T14:34:59","modified_gmt":"2025-05-15T07:34:59","slug":"serum-phuc-hoi-da-gsc-advanced-repair","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-gsc-advanced-repair\/","title":{"rendered":"Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da gsc advanced repair"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm <\/span><\/i><b><i>serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng? D\u00f9 da b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, bong tr\u00f3c hay t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau c\u00e1c li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i serum ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng, c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1eefa v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0? C\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/\"><strong>GSC<\/strong> <\/a>xem ngay nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"serum-phuc-hoi-da-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Serum c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng tinh ch\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu l\u00e0n da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i serum d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng hay ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a. Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap da l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1ee1ng chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2492\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2492\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2492 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot.webp\" alt=\"Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2492\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1ecbp s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh t\u1eeb thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed\u2026 Khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sai c\u00e1ch, ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng y\u1ebfu, d\u1ec5 l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n. M\u1ed9t serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khi-nao-ban-can-mot-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot\"><\/span><b>Khi n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m xoa d\u1ecbu l\u00e0n da. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ngay m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2491\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2491\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2491 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc.webp\" alt=\"Khi n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2491\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Khi n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng: N\u1ebfu da b\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecf, n\u00f3ng r\u00e1t sau khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ho\u1eb7c m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da kh\u00f4, bong tr\u00f3c: Thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4, c\u0103ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb n\u1ee9t n\u1ebb.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da y\u1ebfu sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 peel hay l\u0103n kim th\u00ec da c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1ecb suy y\u1ebfu: Khi da th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&gt;&gt; <\/span><b><i>Xem th\u00eam: Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t 2025<\/i><\/b><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-advanced-repair-serum-%e2%80%93-giai-phap-phuc-hoi-da-chuyen-san\"><\/span><b>GSC Advanced Repair Serum &#8211; Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft n\u00ean tin ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o. Th\u00ec GSC Advanced Repair Serum l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cao c\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t theo c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u00ean men hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i \u01b0u v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2489\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2489\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2489 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/san-pham-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot.webp\" alt=\"Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/san-pham-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/san-pham-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/san-pham-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/san-pham-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/san-pham-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2489\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-nen-chon-gsc-advanced-repair-serum\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn GSC Advanced Repair Serum<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a Bifida Ferment, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t DNA c\u00e1 t\u1ea7m gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ed9 4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng (EGF, bFGF, IGF, aFGF) h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ea3n sinh collagen, l\u00e0m da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt nh\u01b0 b\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i xanh, c\u1ea7n t\u00e2y, c\u00e1m g\u1ea1o gi\u00fap cung c\u1ea5p vitamin v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu cho da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u nh\u1eb9, th\u1ea5m nhanh, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ebft d\u00ednh, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau c\u00e1c li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do corticoid<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a da<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2490\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2490\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2490 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-gsc-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2490\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da GSC<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div class=\"mceTemp\"><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 cho l\u00e0n da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"so-sanh-serum-phuc-hoi-da-gsc-voi-cac-san-pham-khac\"><\/span><b>So s\u00e1nh serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da GSC v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed<\/b><\/td>\n<td><b>Serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><b>GSC Advanced Repair Serum<\/b><\/td>\n<td><b>Serum th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng<\/b><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u00ean men Bifida Ferment, DNA c\u00e1 t\u1ea7m, y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 HA ho\u1eb7c B5<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh, c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da, c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m nh\u1eb9, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e2u<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 da \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da suy y\u1ebfu, nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu d\u00e0nh cho da kh\u00f4<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u l\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u nhanh v\u00e0o da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u1eddn d\u00ednh<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u00f2ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y nh\u1eddn r\u00edt<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2488\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2488\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2488 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot.webp\" alt=\"Routine ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da cao c\u1ea5p\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-serum-phuc-hoi-da-tot-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2488\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Routine ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da cao c\u1ea5p<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">KH 1: Da m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng do d\u00f9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, nh\u01b0ng sau 2 tu\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng GSC Advanced Repair Serum, da m\u00ecnh d\u1ecbu \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t n\u1eefa!&#8221; \u2013 Ng\u1ecdc Mai, 27 tu\u1ed5i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">KH 2: &#8220;M\u00ecnh v\u1eeba l\u00e0m laser tr\u1ecb n\u00e1m, b\u00e1c s\u0129 khuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i. Sau 1 th\u00e1ng d\u00f9ng GSC, da m\u00ecnh kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n bong tr\u00f3c, c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0!&#8221; \u2013 Thanh H\u01b0\u01a1ng, 30 tu\u1ed5i<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da kho\u1ebb l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o trang \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng hay c\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau peel, laser, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ngay m\u1ed9t <\/span><b>serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, <\/span><b>serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> gi\u00fap da t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o nhanh, duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ch\u1ecdn ngay s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2489,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[12],"class_list":["post-2375","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong","tag-lam-dep-da"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2375","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2375"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2375\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3026,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2375\/revisions\/3026"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2489"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2375"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2375"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2375"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}